1.5
log
@RIP mac68k.  No one loves you anymore.
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: scsi_5380.h,v 1.4 2011/03/23 16:54:36 pirofti Exp $	*/
/*	$NetBSD: scsi_5380.h,v 1.3 1994/10/26 08:46:46 cgd Exp $	*/

/*
